Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.03,0:00:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓它陷入了靜寂而永恆的睡眠中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.70,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個森林即使是現在仍然遍佈著堅硬的荊棘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.90,0:00:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地阻止著來自外部的侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.05,0:00:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 會持續到我死亡的時候為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.19,0:02:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}荊棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人她…？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試結束後就是聖誕節呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.62,0:02:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃薔薇大人說結業式時要在薔薇館開個聯歡會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.89,0:02:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.02,0:02:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡聖誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要包裝嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是流言中的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.13,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是放棄讀這本書比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳怎麼想呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.62,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話 會讀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.30,0:03:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方面也有些在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.92,0:03:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先單純地讀讀看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.11,0:03:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣去讀 如果白薔薇大人的事真寫在上面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.87,0:03:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須加星如果是白薔薇大人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概我會更加尊敬她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會請她在文集上簽名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不錯啊 你的這種性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.31,0:03:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 果然對是否讀這本書猶豫不決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荊棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書的作者「須加星」實際上是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.09,0:03:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那個白薔薇大人出版了將自已\n隱藏的過去毫不隱瞞地拼綴起來的自白小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種流言在到處流傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說也只是流言而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.41,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些看過這本叫「大波斯菊通信」的\n新刊導讀雜誌上專題介紹的人們的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.86,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荊棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者 須加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.32,0:04:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學園裡數月的生活是否只是夢幻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖將一切封印在了心中那荊棘的森林中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.18,0:04:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人期待的新人作家 衝擊的自傳性處女作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.85,0:04:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須加星與白薔薇大人的真名「佐藤聖」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確「星」與「聖」發音相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且既然是自傳性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是將自已的過去寫在了這本小說裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會流言四起也是可以理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人過去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為一年級生的由乃你們大概不知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人的過去也可說是禁忌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都儘量不去提及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.55,0:04:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可說是一種「無言的理解」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.14,0:04:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道事情的人大家都三緘其口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像在保護著甚麼似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是發生了甚麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.31,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我是一年級生 沒有被告知詳細的經過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.46,0:05:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去… 是去年的事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.02,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.14,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個白薔薇大人的過去寫在了這本書裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人會猶豫也是不無道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.06,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 大人們想強制把互為摯友的聖與香織分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.93,0:05:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是她們在聖誕夜裡踏上了沒有目的地的旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她們兩人想一起死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但當聖在病院裡醒過來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織已經去往天國了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很常見的結局嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.22,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學 你看到最後都沒哭嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.73,0:05:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有些地方和我與祥子大人很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.66,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 想說的不是小說的內容啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確看了這個後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有流言說作者是白薔薇大人倒也可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.38,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小說的舞台只可能是莉莉安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 令雖然也看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就說「不要再插手這件事」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就當沒有讀過這本小說」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.36,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「完全不想與流言有任何關聯」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.61,0:06:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 祥子大人在買了文集後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺也是對讀還是不讀猶豫不決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了甚麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令甚麼也不肯對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 只有直接去問白薔薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是只有去問白薔薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 志摩子同學也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼…？ 你們不是姐妹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在意嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.50,0:07:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就去比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.37,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.30,0:07:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話 白薔薇大人就會去薔薇館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.49,0:07:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在令大人與祥子大人面前問不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級藤組 佐藤聖同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻到生活指導室來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是因為那本小說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.05,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 祐巳也被傳喚了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.55,0:07:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.21,0:07:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是祐巳將我作為「摟抱魔」告發了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人 您還不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.07,0:08:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我本來還想問您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.44,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「荊棘的森林」的作者\n是否就是白薔薇大人您或是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.94,0:08:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荊棘？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.03,0:08:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去的話一會兒再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.76,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長 中高等部校長 年級主任以及藤組的負責人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「荊棘的森林」已經變成這麼嚴重的問題了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.26,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟往常一樣開朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.66,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像還不知道被傳喚的原因呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.65,0:08:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.23,0:08:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.63,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.75,0:09:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是值得告訴新聞部的東西 我們可是一點兒也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說 幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人退學也無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的學園可是禁止打工的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.76,0:09:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫小說甚麼的明顯是違反了校規啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退學甚麼的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.98,0:09:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果事情變成那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用「莉莉安瓦版」來發起署名活動也無所謂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.44,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫上「請不要將白薔薇大人退學」甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們真的甚麼也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.51,0:09:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法再支撐下去了 快站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在生活指導室裡互相抱著摔在一起可不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉打擾到各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.98,0:10:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.01,0:10:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到\n大家無法抑制的好奇心我還是先報告一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.17,0:10:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 寫「荊棘的森林」的人不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.28,0:10:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 這一次不能向\n莉莉安瓦版提供新聞材料真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,築山三奈子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.01,0:10:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是薔薇館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概大家聽到傳喚的廣播後都在等我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當華麗的傳喚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是從沒有因個人的事情而被傳喚過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有點羡慕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是不敢當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是薔薇大人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒像我這樣慌裡慌張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了生活指導室嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.43,0:11:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.36,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.92,0:11:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上等品真是不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我先報告一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經向祐巳與由乃說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流言中的那本小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是被傳喚的原因嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚地說明不是我寫的之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長為我說了好話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後簡單地就讓我離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已既沒有讀過實物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.83,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且對於那個流傳的謠言也是剛才才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.47,0:12:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你寫的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向聖母瑪莉亞發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.64,0:12:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個話題就到此結束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？ 黃薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.76,0:12:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異議 紅薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.76,0:12:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 該討論一下聖誕節的聯歡會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.12,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.37,0:12:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都未受到流言的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真是自我中心又淺薄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情低落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我臉上的表情又變來變去了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.93,0:12:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想發言嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要睡得迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意見的人要好好地舉起手來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟會為了這種人而煩惱真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手 白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.59,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 在鬧情緒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子 把祐巳借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是沒甚麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.75,0:13:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會脫她的制服或是胡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.37,0:13:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再開玩笑的話 我可要拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.80,0:13:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令 把由乃也借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要由乃願意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼痛快就允諾沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為令明白我不會對由乃淘氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那為甚麼只對我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為反應很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 祥子的反應也很讓人開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是一次捉弄就會有雙倍樂趣的姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.93,0:13:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.23,0:13:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.06,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我成了壞心前輩的餌食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.98,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 後面的收拾就由我們三人來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼後面就拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.73,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳 不要讓白薔薇大人太開心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.78,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.52,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 有需要我幫忙的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.02,0:14:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在看起來也沒甚麼需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.07,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們陪著姐姐真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.09,0:14:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.49,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓志摩子同學跟我們在一起不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.35,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子是那種即使跟她說不要留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她想留下來就會憑自已的意志留下來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.72,0:14:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在帶著那本「荊棘的森林」嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借我一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借倒是沒甚麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想做甚麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是讀它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你以為我會拿它當鍋墊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.73,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼做為回禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面食堂的餐券？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.05,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.16,0:15:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來的時候在自動販賣機那裡幫我買一罐咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你們的份也一起買好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人真是個不可預料的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子同學真是了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能和那種人做姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.74,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在頸上圍上手帕比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣領會弄髒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.19,0:15:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.99,0:15:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.56,0:15:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人究竟是為了甚麼將我們留下來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.89,0:15:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 如果只是為了借「荊棘的森林」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接帶回家去不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.02,0:15:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.41,0:16:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是因為我們太可愛 所以想要請我們吃拉麵嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學 腦筋快成豆腐渣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說是不會買罐裝年糕豆湯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 那個罐裝年糕豆湯甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界上還有這種東西存在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.15,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 白薔薇大人要的咖啡我們可是好好地買來了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.97,0:16:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經把書仔細地讀完了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.85,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為「荊棘的森林」是我寫的\N那些人也許真是有很好的直覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.05,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不是跟我很像嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想問也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會認為寫那本小說的是我的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.05,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是名字同音而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.27,0:17:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點你們也應該有些發覺了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.84,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們毫不掩飾地流露出了那種好奇心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是為了看你們這種表情才說這種話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想說的部份我不會說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.58,0:17:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也沒問題的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.79,0:17:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.28,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為總覺得只有你們不知道不是很不公平嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.96,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了告訴我們才將我們留下來的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.80,0:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也是為了想早點讀到這本書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓉子與令她們之所以不向你們說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.98,0:17:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也許是為了體諒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.63,0:17:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那麼痛苦的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.28,0:17:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾有過一個非常要好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說她甚至比父母和兄弟更加重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡她到只要有她在 其它甚麼也不需要的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.10,0:17:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個想著將來成為修女的純潔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.91,0:18:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在去年的聖誕節裡 她離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.57,0:18:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全是「荊棘的森林」的聖與香織嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是完全相同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.45,0:18:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既沒有與那個朋友一起踏上旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有吞下安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她轉學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.67,0:18:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說香織還活著了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼呀 還活著很失望嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.55,0:18:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.68,0:18:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 難道是誰以白薔薇大人\N的事作為參考而寫下了這本小說嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.83,0:18:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既有不同的部份 也有相似得驚人的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得生氣嗎 白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自已的過去被擅自寫成了小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.68,0:18:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被人誤認為是作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.90,0:18:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 只要能被最重要的人理解就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想講給你們倆聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.29,0:19:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我討厭殘留著誤解與臆測的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.02,0:19:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉學的朋友 現在怎麼樣了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.48,0:19:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.43,0:19:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想見她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不見面 為好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.06,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的名字 不是香織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.59,0:19:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs52}而是久保 {\fs39\fnsimhei}栞{\r}…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.70,0:19:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人現在還喜歡著那個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也這樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才沒有留下志摩子同學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.96,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會對志摩子同學很過意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.02,0:19:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明會有因小說而受到傷害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.34,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫那本小說的不會是久保{\fs39\fnsimhei}栞{\r}吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.37,0:20:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.73,0:20:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會徹底查明寫這本「荊棘的森林」的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是大波斯菊編輯部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.42,0:20:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼要把我也拉來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.06,0:20:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令也很在意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「荊棘的森林」的作者到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉在忙碌的時候來打擾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 你是「荊棘的森林」的負責人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.38,0:20:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不能將須加星的真實身份告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.19,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天 來自莉莉安學生們的詢問接連不斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.38,0:20:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「須加星的真實身份是否是佐藤聖」之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.22,0:20:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.63,0:20:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真令人懷念啊 這種制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到會在這種地方遇到後輩們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.73,0:21:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.98,0:21:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這麼說您是莉莉安的畢業生了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是很久以前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.13,0:21:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是須加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.51,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本名是春日誠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.28,0:21:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼「荊棘的森林」的舞台果然是莉莉安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前發生的事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.73,0:21:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「荊棘的森林」是在如今\n連傳聞都未留下的很久以前發生的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.17,0:21:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟白薔薇大人的故事就像是其它的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.68,0:21:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有從嘴裡說出她的名字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.51,0:21:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.34,0:21:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今年開始進入莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.68,0:22:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.93,0:23:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 花瓣的瓣是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.23,0:23:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個「瓣」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.82,0:23:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是拘泥在一些古怪的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓣的瓣寫成漢字就是便當的「便」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.54,topfont,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：日語中花瓣的「瓣」與便當的「便」同形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.56,0:23:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當的「便」嗎 原來如此 是便當的「便」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.65,0:23:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周明明是個好故事 真覺得有點被糟塌啦
